h4. Actor:
Administrator, Remittance User, Branch User.

h4. Description:
Name of use case represent its functionality.

h4. Flow:
* Actor clicks [ARMS|guide:_ShowARMSPlugin] option from top menu bar.
* Click "Help Desk" sub menu from left menu.
* Click "Search Beneficiary" link.
* [Show Landing Page of Search Beneficiary|guide:_ShowBeneficiaryDetailsActionService].
* User must insert valid input.
* Click "Search" button.
* [Search Beneficiary|guide:SearchBeneficiaryDetailsActionService].
* Select a *Beneficiary* from *Beneficiary* list.
* Click "View Details" button from tool bar.
* Right side of grid view will show "Beneficiary Task Details".

h4. Pre-condition: 
* User must have "Show Task Details" privilege.

h4. Process:
* Show "Beneficiary Task Details" information.
* Following information should show in grid view:
** Task Details
** Beneficiary Information
** Sender Information

h4. Post-condition:

* *Success:*
** Show the "Beneficiary Task Details" in grid view.

* *Failure:*
** Show error message for details visit [Error Handler|common Usecases].

